# Linear Personal API Key
#
# Get yours at: https://linear.app/settings/api
#   1. Click "Create new API key"
#   2. Give it a name (e.g. "claude-pm-skill")
#   3. Scopes: Read + Write
#   4. Copy the key (starts with `lin_api_`)
#
# Then:
#   1. Copy this file to ~/.claude/secrets/linear-pak.env
#   2. Replace REPLACE_ME with your actual key
#   3. chmod 600 ~/.claude/secrets/linear-pak.env  (Linux/Mac)
#
# NEVER commit this file with a real key.

LINEAR_API_KEY=lin_api_REPLACE_ME
